item.title: About
item.description: Hello friend. Hello friend? That’s lame. Maybe I should give you a name. But that’s a slippery slope, you’re only in my head. We have to remember that. Shit, it’s actually happening. I’m talking to an imaginery person. My name is Yusuf Kaan Ocak. I am a programmer, game developer and a shitty pixel artist (really shitty). Here are some projects I made earlier: https://github.com/lvlzyro/Celeste-Movement https://github.com/lvlzyro/advent-of-code https://github.com/lvlzyro/8-Directional-Movement I don’t know why you are here.
